txt.en: Dráttur is in Amdân.\n\nYou should bring the meat to Dráttur.
'Ah, what a profitable hunt! Though we may die tomorrow, we shall dine well this night.'

'Killing Orcs is hungry work, and we have quite a few mouths to feed. Luckily, the valley provides... in spite of the foul weather. Go hunt moose, deer, and boar, so that we may continue hunting Orcs.'
Keeping a dwarf army fed is a strenuous task. Luckily, the valley of Azanulbizar has a wide range of animals to hunt.
Moose, deer, and wild boar can be found throughout the woods of Azanulbizar.\n\nDráttur has tasked you with hunting the woods for meat to feed the army.
